title: [1508428454] Smoked Haddock & Spinach Baked Eggs | Gordon Ramsay
description:
A brilliantly flavourful and sustainable fish - haddock is a great breakfast choice. Served with a simple spring onion garnish -  this is a hearty breakfast to start any day.
